description:
Potential sensitive configuration items were identified in the FTP server configuration file:  
1) anonymous_enable=NO (anonymous access disabled);  
2) local_enable=YES (local user login permitted);  
3) write_enable=YES (write operations allowed);  
4) chroot_local_user=YES (users restricted to their home directories);  
5) Port range configuration (pasv_min_port=50000, pasv_max_port=60000) may expose a specific port range.
